@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_niapah(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.30)) / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.66) * (v1 + 0.43 * v0 + 0.23)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v1 - 0.32))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.96 * v1 + 0.77)) / wp.cos((v1 + 0.47 + v2 + 0.15)))
    tmp = 0.69
    tmp = wp.cos((0.30 + wp.abs(v2 + 0.36)))
    data[tid] = v0
